						<summary>

						<p>On a stone set up near the Viśvanāthasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 14 • • • • • • • • • ., Śrāvaṇa śu. 13.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the remission of taxes on barbers in Koṇḍavīṭi-sīma by Rāmappayya who was administering the district.</p>						

